data.description: Welcome to this beautiful investment property in Mt. Washington. Very well maintained brick duplex. Walking distance to Grandview Avenue,  the Duquesne incline and Emerald View park. Convenient to the South Side, downtown, Station Square and the North Shore. The property is tenant occupied and rarely vacant. Each unit is 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, back decks on each unit and a shared basement with a washer and dryer included. Fully equipped kitchens with appliances being less than a year old. Property has a nice level lot. This property is great for renters as it includes an integral double car garage and 3 off-street parking spaces.
